Rewe Group Full-Year Revenue Rises 4% on Domestic Supermarkets

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-02-25T08:36:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/rewe-group-full-year-revenue-rises-4-on-domestic-supermarkets.html
Rewe Group,  Germany ’s second-largest
food retailer, said full-year revenue rose 4 percent to a record
53 billion euros ($73 billion).  The increase was driven by growth in the closely held
company’s domestic supermarket business, Cologne-based Rewe said
in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story: 
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 